<h1 class="to-animate">The Mental Health &amp; Psychosocial Support Network</h1>
<h2 class="to-animate">A growing global platform for connecting people, networks and organizations, for sharing resources and for building knowledge related to mental health and psychosocial support both in emergency settings and in situations of chronic hardship. The network functions as an online community of practice for mental health and psychosocial support in challenging humanitarian and development contexts.</h2>
